raziel ( " secret[s ] of god " ) is an archangel within the teachings of jewish mysticism ( of the kabbalah of judaism ) who is the " keeper of secrets " and the " angel of mysteries".davidson , gustav ( 1967 ) , a dictionary of angels , including the fallen angels , entry : raziel , free press , pp .

chris & tell : in a christopher moore tale , christmas is thrown into chaos by raziel , " the stupidest " of these winged beings

